name: STONEFISH AI
description: The most venomous fish in the world is ready to take over SUI ocean. Purpose of the project is to be a useful MEME AI in different social media. Function of stonefish ai is to be an AI and to design and autonomous systems that operate in the background carrying out tasks without active human intervention. These system would be invisible in the that they are integrated into a larger process and ensuring efficiency without requiring constant oversight.
